Class NomenclatureItem

java.lang.Object
  com.onwbp.base.text.NomenclatureItem
Direct Known Subclasses:
NomenclatureItemValue
public abstract class NomenclatureItem
extends Object

A NomenclatureItem associates a value with one or more labels. Each label may be associated with a locale.
